### Xfinity Home Security

## Home monitoring you can count on

Protect your home with 24/7 professional monitoring for the ultimate security solution.

$45/mo

[Shop home security](https://www.xfinity.com/digital/offers/plan-builder "Shop home security")

[Sign in to add](http://xfinity.com/buy/plan/offersfilter?upgrade=true&intcmp=ILC:UPS:BAUP:SUB:GEN:XH:COM:NA:cry:9161082552 "Sign in to add")

Includes $10/mo. auto-pay & paperless bill discount. Equipment sold separately. Pricing subject to change. Taxes and fees extra.

## Safety starts here

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_Agent_60.png)

Professional protection 24/7

Best-in-class monitoring so you can rest assured knowing help is just a moment away.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_CloudStorage_60.png)

Accessible cloud storage

With top-tier cloud storage, your video footage is easily searchable and securely stored for up to a week.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_Lightning_60.svg)

Outage protection

Cellular battery backup for protection, even during in outages.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_Verify_60.svg)

Control on-the-go

Access connected smart home devices wherever you are.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_Contract_60.svg)

No strings attached

Start with any Home System, and join today without a contract.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_3/2025/jan/cix-7932_xfinity-pro-protection-plus-rebrand-to-xfinity-home-security/Icon_Devices_60.svg)

Access all over the house

Control on your TV with Xfinity Voice Remote.

Viewing and recording video requires an Xfinity camera or video doorbell.

## Your connected home. Your way.

Customize your system with Xfinity equipment or connect compatible devices from popular brands — and control it all using the Xfinity app.

[Shop Xfinity Equipment](https://www.xfinity.com/learn/home-security/devices "Shop Xfinity Equipment")

[Check compatibility](https://www.xfinity.com/learn/home-security/our-partners "Check compatibility")

Smart home device integration with the Xfinity app requires a compatible Xfinity Gateway and Self Protection or Xfinity Home Security.

# Self Protection

## Keep an eye on your home from anywhere

Build your smart home protection system with video doorbells, locks, and indoor/outdoor cameras — and manage it all from the Xfinity app.

$10/mo

[Build your plan](https://www.xfinity.com/digital/offers/plan-builder "Build your plan")

[Sign in to add](https://www.xfinity.com/buy/plan/internet/self-protection "Sign in to add")

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/icon-1.svg)

## Select a plan

from deals in your area that fit your needs.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/icon-2.svg)

for seamless integration with Xfinity camera devices.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/icon-3.svg)

with no-term contract and add any other equipment you need.

For just $5/month each for 24 months, Xfinity Outdoor Cameras automatically connect to your Xfinity Gateway and Xfinity Home app, indoors or outdoors.\*

### Kwikset Smart Lock

## Let friends and family in from anywhere

Add up to 3 smart locks to Self Protection for just $5/mo each for 24 months, and keep your doors secure with the Xfinity Home app.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/kwickset/icon-real-time.svg)

Real-Time Lock & Unlock Notifications

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/kwickset/icon-eaisily-upgrade.svg)

Easily Upgrade Your Current Compatible Lock

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/icons/kwickset/lock.svg)

Auto-Locks To Stay Secure, Even When You Forget

[Shop home solutions](https://www.xfinity.com/digital/offers/plan-builder "Shop home solutions")

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/half-image-5-left-dt.jpg)

### Kwikset Smart Lock + Xfinity Camera

## See and control your door all at once

Save on a camera and smart lock with the Xfinity Smart Entry Kit, just $9/mo for 24 months. See who's at the door and let them in or keep it locked, all from the Xfinity Home app.

[Shop home solutions](https://www.xfinity.com/digital/offers/plan-builder "Shop home solutions")

### Customize your setup

## Build the right system for you

We've partnered with popular smart home brands, so you can combine your Xfinity equipment with your favorite smart devices. Connect them through the xFi Gateway – no smart hub needed – and control it all from the Xfinity Home app.

![](https://assets.xfinity.com/assets/dotcom/projects_2/cix-6462_xh-self-protection-page-redesign---new-customer/product-image-lock-dt.jpg)

Locks

[See compatible locks](https://www.xfinity.com/learn/home-solutions/self-protection#Seecompatiblelocks "See compatible locks")

Thermostats

[See compatible thermostats](https://www.xfinity.com/learn/home-solutions/self-protection#Seecompatiblethermostats "See compatible thermostats")
